title: Big Data Cybersecurity Analysis Paper
description: A joint-research project conducted on a large dataset containing 18.5+ million records of network intrusions labelled by the MITRE ATT&CK framework. Using Support Vector Machine (SVM) for multinomial classification on the raw dataset to evaluate its performance and support evidence for a related paper, comparing other machine learning algorithms and preprocessing techniques.
